Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:32.27,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:43.24,OP_ED_ZH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur3}你的氣味 令人發狂
